a®</a>.</p>\n\n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"\n            \n                                \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"name\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Jeremy Holcombe\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}s:6:\"source\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"\n                    \n                            \n                \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:2:{s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://kinsta.com/fr/blog/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Kinsta\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n    \n            \n                \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:9:{s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://holdmywp.com/ameliorer-le-wp-config-php/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:27:\"Améliorer le wp-config.php\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:4:\"href\";s:48:\"https://holdmywp.com/ameliorer-le-wp-config-php/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:9:\"alternate\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"updated\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"2025-07-25T11:13:19.000+00:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"published\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"2025-07-25T11:13:19.000+00:00\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"summary\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:141:\"Un ensemble de constantes WordPress pour pimper son fichier wp-config.php, améliorer les performances et la sécurité de son site internet.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18178:\"\n        \n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Un ensemble de constantes WordPress pour pimper son fichier <code>wp-config.php</code>, améliorer les performances et la <a href=\"https://holdmywp.com/checklist-securite-wordpress/\" title=\"Ma check-list de sécurité WordPress ✅\">sécurité</a> de son site internet.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"#extrait-de-code-complet\">Voir le code complet ↓</a></div>\n</div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"securite\">Sécurité</h2>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"environnement\">Environnement</h3>\n\n\n<p>Constante par défaut pour préciser l&rsquo;environnement dans lequel le code est exécuté, chez certains hébergeurs, influe sur le comportement et l&rsquo;affichage d&rsquo;erreurs. Je préfère le définir clairement dans mon fichier <code>wp-config.php</code>.</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_ENVIRONMENT_TYPE\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'production\'</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"url\">URL</h3>\n\n\n<p>Permets d&#8217;empêcher de changer le nom de domaine du site depuis l&rsquo;interface d&rsquo;administration.</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_HOME\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'https://website.domain/\'</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_SITEURL\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'https://website.domain/\'</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"ssl\">SSL</h3>\n\n\n<p>Force l&rsquo;accès à l&rsquo;interface d&rsquo;administration en HTTPS.</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'FORCE_SSL_LOGIN\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'FORCE_SSL_ADMIN\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"debogage\">Débogage</h3>\n\n\n<p>Désactive les fonctions de débogage de WordPress. Permets notamment d&rsquo;éviter d&rsquo;afficher les erreurs sur l&rsquo;interface publique.</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_DEBUG\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_DEBUG_LOG\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_DEBUG_DISPLAY\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"mises-a-jour\">Mises à jour</h3>\n\n\n<p>Force les mises à jour automatiques mineures du cœur de WordPress, et évite le téléchargement des nouveaux thèmes par défaut.</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_AUTO_UPDATE_CORE\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'minor\'</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'CORE_UPGRADE_SKIP_NEW_BUNDLED\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"reparation-de-la-base-de-donnee\">Réparation de la base de donnée</h3>\n\n\n<p>Empêche l&rsquo;accès à l&rsquo;outil natif de WordPress de réparation de la base de donnée.</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_ALLOW_REPAIR\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"inclusion-de-code\">Inclusion de code</h3>\n\n\n<p>Empêche de coller et d&rsquo;exécuter du code « à l&rsquo;arrache » dans l&rsquo;éditeur. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><mark class=\"has-inline-color has-red-color\">⚠️ Peux poser un problème avec certaines extensions ou thèmes qui affichent des SVG.</mark></p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'DISALLOW_UNFILTERED_HTML\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"edition-du-code\">Édition du code</h3>\n\n\n<p>Empêche l&rsquo;édition des fichiers du site depuis l&rsquo;interface d&rsquo;administration</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'DISALLOW_FILE_EDIT\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"fichiers-mis-en-ligne\">Fichiers mis en ligne</h3>\n\n\n<p>Désactive les téléchargements non filtrés, empêchant les téléchargements de fichiers dangereux.</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'ALLOW_UNFILTERED_UPLOADS\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"performances\">Performances</h2>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"cache\">Cache</h3>\n\n\n<p>Si défini, WordPress tentera de charger le fichier <code>/wp-content/advanced-cache.php</code> lors du chargement de la page. Permets d&rsquo;activer les fonctionnalités des extensions de cache comme <a href=\"https://holdmywp.com/comment-configurer-cache-enabler/\" title=\"Comment configurer Cache Enabler\">Cache Enabler</a>.</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_CACHE\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"memoire\">Mémoire</h3>\n\n\n<p>Ces constantes définissent les limites de mémoire pour l&rsquo;interface publique (<code>WP_MEMORY_LIMIT</code>) et l&rsquo;interface d&rsquo;administration (<code>WP_MAX_MEMORY_LIMIT</code>). Je les aligne au plus proche de la mémoire allouée dans le <code class=\"\">php.ini</code>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress utilise des valeurs par défaut (40MB) et vérifie la configuration du serveur pour ajuster ces limites. En les définissant directement, on évite la vérification de configuration et les erreurs, optimise l&rsquo;utilisation des ressources de l&rsquo;hébergement et améliore ainsi les performances globales du site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>En général, l&rsquo;interface d&rsquo;administration aura besoin de plus de ressources.</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_MAX_MEMORY_LIMIT\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'128M\'</span>); <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Mettre 256M pour un site WooCommerce</span>\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_MEMORY_LIMIT\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'40M\'</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"compression-et-concatenation\">Compression et concaténation</h3>\n\n\n<p>Force l&rsquo;utilisation des scripts JS minifiés, active la minification des styles et des scripts par WordPress, charge les scripts dans des fichiers concaténés, active <a href=\"https://holdmywp.com/cache-wordpress-super-rapide/\" title=\"Un cache WordPress super rapide (et gratuit) sans WP Rocket\">la compression GZIP</a>.</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'SCRIPT_DEBUG\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'CONCATENATE_SCRIPTS\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'COMPRESS_SCRIPTS\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'COMPRESS_CSS\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'ENFORCE_GZIP\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"sauvegarde-automatique\">Sauvegarde automatique</h3>\n\n\n<p>Définie la sauvegarde automatique à cinq minutes (au lieu d&rsquo;une minute par défaut), réduit la charge serveur.</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'AUTOSAVE_INTERVAL\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">300</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"cron-wordpress\">Cron WordPress</h3>\n\n\n<p><mark class=\"has-inline-color has-red-color\">⚠️ Mettre en place seulement si on peut configurer un cron directement sur l&rsquo;hébergement (plus robuste et efficace), désactive le cron natif de WordPress pour ne pas faire doublon.</mark></p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'DISABLE_WP_CRON\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"bonus-constantes-dextensions\">Bonus : constantes d&rsquo;extensions</h2>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"contact-form-7\">Contact Form 7</h3>\n\n\n<p>Contact Form 7 charge par défaut ses scripts et styles sur toutes les pages du site, je désactive ce comportement globalement et inclus ces fichiers seulement sur les pages qui le nécessitent.</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">define(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WPCF7_LOAD_JS\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WPCF7_LOAD_CSS\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"sqlite-object-cache\">SQLite Object Cache</h3>\n\n\n<p>Active le cache objet avec APCU sur <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/sqlite-object-cache/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"SQLite Object Cache\">SQLite Object Cache</a>.</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/** Object cache **/</span>\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_SQLITE_OBJECT_CACHE_APCU\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"zenpress\">ZenPress</h3>\n\n\n<p>L&rsquo;extension <a href=\"https://holdmywp.com/zenpress/\" title=\"ZenPress – Unbloat, Performance &amp; Security\">ZenPress</a> que je développe est paramétrable avec les constantes WordPress. Sur les sites de type blog, je laisse la fonctionnalité de flux RSS active.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-fg-2-background-color has-background has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"border-top-color:var(--wp--preset--color--violet);border-top-width:0.18rem;border-right-color:var(--wp--preset--color--violet);border-right-width:0.18rem;border-bottom-color:var(--wp--preset--color--violet);border-bottom-width:0.18rem;border-left-color:var(--wp--preset--color--violet);border-left-width:0.96rem\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-bd3f9bef wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-bg-0-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-7e04d43aa399da37ac6c60a62204e66c is-vertical is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-43ece9da wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\">\n<p class=\"has-bg-0-color has-text-color has-link-color has-outfit-font-family has-large-font-size wp-elements-17ca34d4cb992131934b342e15a269c5\" style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:700\">Besoin de plus de performances ?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Découvre <strong>ZenPress</strong>, mon extension ultralégère gratuite pour débarrasser ton site WordPress des fonctions inutiles et des publicités, améliorer la sécurité et les performances.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-left is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-0076338b wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/zenpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Page WordPress.org</a></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https://holdmywp.com/zenpress/\">Documentation</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/** ZenPress **/</span>\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'ZENPRESS_DISABLE_RSS\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);</code></span></pre>\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"extrait-de-code-complet\">Extrait de code complet</h2>\n\n\n<p>Voilà ma section pour optimiser les performances et la sécurité d&rsquo;un site WordPress à insérer dans la partie dédiée à la personnalisation du fichier <code>wp-config.php</code>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Attention à bien la modifier selon les besoins de ton site.</p>\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><span><code class=\"hljs language-php\">\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* Add any custom values between this line and the \"stop editing\" line. */</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* ————————————————\n * Security\n * ———————————————— */</span>\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_ENVIRONMENT_TYPE\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'production\'</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_HOME\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'https://website.domain/\'</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_SITEURL\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'https://website.domain/\'</span>);\n\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'FORCE_SSL_LOGIN\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'FORCE_SSL_ADMIN\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\n\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_DEBUG\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_DEBUG_LOG\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_DEBUG_DISPLAY\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);\n\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_AUTO_UPDATE_CORE\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'minor\'</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'CORE_UPGRADE_SKIP_NEW_BUNDLED\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\n\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_ALLOW_REPAIR\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);\n\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'DISALLOW_UNFILTERED_HTML\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'DISALLOW_FILE_EDIT\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\n\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'ALLOW_UNFILTERED_UPLOADS\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* ————————————————\n * Performances\n * ———————————————— */</span>\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_MEMORY_LIMIT\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'40M\'</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_MAX_MEMORY_LIMIT\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\'128M\'</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'AUTOSAVE_INTERVAL\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">300</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_CACHE\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\n\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'SCRIPT_DEBUG\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'CONCATENATE_SCRIPTS\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'COMPRESS_SCRIPTS\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'COMPRESS_CSS\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'ENFORCE_GZIP\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\n\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'DISABLE_WP_CRON\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* ————————————————\n * Plugins\n * ———————————————— */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*** Contact form 7 ***/</span>\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WPCF7_LOAD_JS\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WPCF7_LOAD_CSS\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*** Object cache ***/</span>\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'WP_SQLITE_OBJECT_CACHE_APCU\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">true</span>);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*** ZenPress ***/</span>\ndefine(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\'ZENPRESS_DISABLE_RSS\'</span>, <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>);\n\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* That\'s all, stop editing! Happy publishing. */</span>\n</code></span></pre>\n\n\n<p>J&rsquo;espère que cette publication t&rsquo;aidera. Si tu as des questions, besoin de <a href=\"https://holdmywp.com/maintenance-wordpress/\" title=\"Maintenance WordPress\">support</a> sur ton site WordPress, ou que tu veux apporter ta contribution, n&rsquo;hésite pas à me <a href=\"https://holdmywp.com/contact/\" title=\"Me contacter\">contacter</a> ou à laisser un petit commentaire !</p>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"sources\">Sources</h2>\n\n\n<p>➡️ <a href=\"https://developer.wordpress.org/advanced-administration/wordpress/wp-config/#increasing-memory-allocated-to-php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"https://developer.wordpress.org/advanced-administration/wordpress/wp-config/\">https://developer.wordpress.org/advanced-administration/wordpress/wp-config/</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>➡️ <a href=\"https://wp-kama.com/1588/wordpress-constants\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"https://wp-kama.com/1588/wordpress-constants#wp_debug\">https://wp-kama.com/1588/wordpress-constants</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>➡️ <a href=\"https://www.php.net/manual/en/ini.core.php#ini.memory-limit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">https://www.php.net/manual/en/ini.core.php#ini.memory-limit</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>➡️ <a href=\"https://contactform7.com/loading-javascript-and-stylesheet-only-when-it-is-necessary/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">https://contactform7.com/loading-javascript-and-stylesheet-only-when-it-is- necessary/</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://holdmywp.com/ameliorer-le-wp-config-php/\">Source</a></p>\n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"\n            \n                 